# Welcome to mod_gmi2html

A powerful Apache module that converts Gemini format documents to HTML.

## What is Gemini?

Gemini is a lightweight markup language designed for personal publishing on the web. It sits between plain text and Markdown in terms of complexity.

## Features of This Module

* Fast conversion from .gmi to HTML
* Full Gemini specification support
* Apache 2.4+ compatibility
* Easy to configure and deploy

